strings: <voice_0x010016BF><se_low>January: Hi, how long have I known you? !!! I haven't seen your face since I killed that fat guy.
<voice_0x010016C6><se_low>January: I will do my best to support your first big work!
<voice_0x010016C7><se_low>January: This is our dear Ozpin, listen to me! You're no longer a "horse", are you?
<voice_0x010016C8><se_low>January: So are you going with the princess to a "wedding" at Sèvres Cathedral?
<voice_0x010016C9><se_low>January: But I still do not understand why she married a common man.
<voice_0x010016CA><se_low>January: to do! Almost forgot us! You must receive a letter from an old priest you met on the road.
<voice_0x010016CB><se_low>January: I thought the princess was going out, so I met her in her room.
<voice_0x010016CC><se_low>January: Why not relax in the garden See you
<voice_0x010016C0><se_high>Dye: Wow, you haven't seen Flamin in a year. I meant I know you are calm. but even so...
<voice_0x010016C1><se_high>Dye: "I called to find someone to call."
<voice_0x010016C2><se_high>Dye: A true goddess<:> "When she came to me, the first thing she said to me was, 'Has God forgotten me?'"
<voice_0x010016C3><se_low>January: Hey redheads, turn the volume down!
<voice_0x010016C5><se_low>January: Bye... Anyway, boss, I heard the news. chief of bodyguards? Aren't things better? but you deserve this
